            "title": "特朗普與埃爾多安會晤後 土耳其宣布大筆訂購波音飛機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普與埃爾多安會晤後 土耳其宣布大筆訂購波音飛機\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ljVNBPoiGEqedjAOu1t1SQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/b512a3c0-9ad3-11f0-8fbf-83b6b4633ac0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普與埃爾多安會晤後 土耳其宣布大筆訂購波音飛機</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
