        {
            "title": "小米董事長雷軍承諾加快提升YU7電動汽車的產量",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 小米公司聯合創始人雷軍誓言要加快提升YU7電動汽車的產量。這款新車型在上市不到三個月內已交付逾4萬輛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小米董事長、執行長雷軍周四在小米新機發布會上表示，「YU7在發布後18小時內鎖單突破24萬輛，創下行業紀錄。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位億萬富豪補充稱：「我們自7月6日開始交付YU7，截至目前已過去2個月零19天，交付量超過4萬輛。我知道這與大家的期待仍有差距，我們會繼續努力。」小米一位代表周五拒絕進一步置評。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a2542e11-4305-3d46-9ab0-e71e19be98b8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">起家於智慧手機的小米正儘可能快地提升電動汽車產能，以滿足超出預期的需求。分析師關注小米能否順利完成產能爬坡，這將決定小米在中國白熱化的汽車市場中的競爭力。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"小米押注電動汽車，挑戰特斯拉。資料來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nbtly.7ZsRGSGBhpZiql7w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6da4420944e45f54b7359e05080f8276\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">小米押注電動汽車，挑戰特斯拉。資料來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多功能運動車YU7當前的生產速度略快於小米首款電動車型SU7，生產首批10萬輛SU7用時230天。由於車身更大、結構更複雜，YU7的組裝時間可能也更長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小米汽車App顯示，如果現在下單，YU7預計交付周期為45至48周，較上月預計的56至59周有所縮短。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：雷軍發布起售價4499元的小米手機 挑戰蘋果iPhone 17系列</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Xiaomi Pledges to Spur Production Efforts for YU7 Electric Car</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Jessica Sui、Charlotte Yang、Linda Lew.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7%E9%9B%B7%E8%BB%8D%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87yu7%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F-053712534.html",
