            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "北歐交易熱潮引華爾街銀行垂涎 人才爭奪升溫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著北歐掀起交易熱潮，從Evercore Inc.到Lazard Inc.的一些投資銀行紛紛在該地區挖人，試圖從本土競爭對手那裡搶奪市場占有率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Evercore上個月聘用了前花旗集團北歐投資銀行主管Lars Ingemarsson，讓他領導其位於斯德哥爾摩的新辦公室、建立一支由15名銀行家組成的團隊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lazard招募了過去十年就職於羅斯柴爾德的Jesper Jensen，要在哥本哈根開設新辦公室。該行歐洲投資銀行聯席主管Jean-Louis Girodolle稱，他們正在那裡組建一個五到六人的團隊。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c9e46dd4-827e-3c57-be14-53f8430fd4e2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，Thomas Westin最近從高盛集團跳槽PJT Partners Inc.，受命在斯德哥爾摩組建一支團隊。羅斯柴爾德本月挖走了DNB Carnegie Holding AB的Miro Hemanus，闖進赫爾辛基。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的數據顯示，北歐國家（包括瑞典、丹麥、芬蘭、挪威和冰島）今年以來已宣布超過1200億美元的交易，連續第十年超過1000億美元。數據顯示，該地區也超過了法國這個歐洲歷來的最大併購市場之一，後者今年宣布的交易總額約為1050億美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LxTdsil71jxcE5dgIXlkpA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4525a375176aff822c6b1ec37afe624e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Wall Street Banks Fight for Talent in Nordics as M&amp;A Heats Up</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Evelina Youcefi.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
